# Title: Recon Information for Export with PowerShell
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2021-07-30
# Level: medium
# Description: Once established within a system or network, an adversary may use automated techniques for collecting internal data
# MITRE Tactic: Collection
# Tags: attack.collection, attack.t1119
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_susp_recon_export.yml

ScriptBlockText IN ("*Get-Service *", "*Get-ChildItem *", "*Get-Process *") ScriptBlockText="*> $env:TEMP\\*"